hello I'm Cooper from the AWS account
and billing support team in North
America today I'll show you how to apply
AWS promotional credits to your AWS
account let's get started promotional
credit codes can be redeemed under the
credit section in your billing and cost
management Council in just a few
steps to start open the billing and cost
management
Council next select credits on the left
side of the
screen now on the top right choose the
orange redeem credit
button then enter your promotional
credit code make sure that you don't add
spaces or special characters before or
after the code when you enter it enter
the characters as shown in the security
check box then choose redeem at the
bottom of the page if you enter the code
correctly the code is valid and the code
was not previously redeemed then it's
added automatic atically to your AWS
account so now you know how to apply AWS
promotional credits to your AWS account
thanks for watching and happy cloud
computing from all of us here at
